OL,3,CKirkup 'disappointed' with response to
OL,4,Cmedical negligence claims
OL,6,FHSJ reported that families will have
OL,7,Fto prove liability for the harm caused
OL,8,Fbefore getting compensation, including
OL,9,Fin a number of cases where the inquiry
OL,10,Fconcluded that there could have been a
OL,11,Fdifferent outcome with better care.
OL,13,FDr Kirkup told HSJ, "I am disappointed
OL,14,Fthat East Kent families are facing
OL,15,Fthese problems after everything that
OL,16,Fhas happened to them. Of course, it is
OL,17,Ftrue that the independent
OL,18,Finvestigation panel was not in a
OL,19,Fposition to rule on negligence, but we
OL,20,Fdid provide a robust clinical
OL,21,Fassessment of each case."
OL,26,@uD@UOU
