OL,3,CKirkup 'disappointed' with response to
OL,4,Cmedical negligence claims
OL,6,F"I would have hoped that this could be
OL,7,Ftaken into account in deciding to
OL,8,Foffer early settlement instead of a
OL,9,Fprotracted dispute."
OL,11,F"It seems sad that a more
OL,12,Fcompassionate approach has not been
OL,13,Fadopted."
OL,15,FIt is understood that a number of
OL,16,Fcases have been resolved but other
OL,17,Ffamilies are still going through the
OL,18,Fclaims process with NHS Resolution,
OL,19,Fwhich handles claims for clinical
OL,20,Fnegligence.
