OL,6,FAn NHS Resolution spokesperson said,
OL,7,F"NHS Resolution aims to resolve all
OL,8,Fclaims for compensation quickly and
OL,9,Ffairly and on their individual merits."
OL,11,F"This involves reviewing the evidence
OL,12,Fon each case, including inquiry
OL,13,Ffindings, if they are shared, to
OL,14,Fdetermine whether the care was
OL,15,Fnegligent and caused harm to a
OL,16,Fpatient."
