OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said, "Minister (Maria)
OL,8,FCaulfield has met with many families
OL,9,Finvolved in the East Kent maternity
OL,10,Finquiry over the past year to hear
OL,11,Ftheir concerns, alongside the local
OL,12,FEast Kent regional group, which meets
OL,13,Fregularly to ensure the
OL,14,Frecommendations and findings from the
OL,15,FEast Kent Report are being acted on,
OL,16,Fand services are improving."
OL,18,F"NHS Resolution manages clinical
OL,19,Fnegligence and other claims against
OL,20,Fthe NHS in England."
